reviews.text: Geese fat with noodles are the special dish in this restaurant,  must try and the price are acceptable.

The BBQ pork was good at well as the beef stomach. I'll probably cook it a little longer. The noodle with goose oil flavor was very flavorful.  

The hamf shredded chicken is a must try. Mic drop. 

I ordered the milk tea and it was also very delightful.  Love HK/Macau when almost everyone can make a good cup of HK style milktea.
you could try if u like goose oil noodle, not really impress
Providing tasty snack
Excellent rice combo love the noodles and shredded chicken

reviews.text: 幾十年的老店👍👍👍遊荃灣必打卡😋
又一間不錯的小店，用心經營，食物水準穩定。鵝油撈麵、炆豬手、手撕雞都是返店首選。雖然今次的雞咸了－点，但仍然有鮮味和嫩滑。豬手濃香而軟滑，鵝油麵香雖油膩一點。
地方不算大，但食物是OK唔錯的。
個撈麵食得吓， 其他都只係一般。
豬手捞粗，豬手唔夠霖，粗麵冇味
